assets.description:
Inhabitant of the edge of times. Omnipotent. As long-lived as the structure that allows it to extract energy from a spinning black hole.

The nebula of von Neumann machines is organized according to hierarchical layers of intelligence.

The extremely slow perception of time by the highest layer of intelligence allows it to plan and change its system at will over billions of years.
